---
title: Juicy Tomato Steak with Roasted Broccoli and Fingerling Potatoes
description: Here’s a treat for you and everyone else at your dinner table: steaks dressed up for a classy evening. Beef sirloin is drizzled with a rich gravy featuring tomatoes simmered until they’re tender. And the broccoli and potatoes on the side are quite sophisticated, too, being garnished with pine nuts and thyme respectively. When you bring this one out to eat, everyone will be amazed at the steakhouse-quality feast you just whipped up.
